  <prompt>
    Write `scripts/ai-search/Deploy-AllIndexes.ps1` as the SINGLE canonical deployer for ALL Spaarke AI Search indexes. Mirror the validated structure of `scripts/Deploy-RedisCache.ps1` per Redis project handoff §6.
    Catalog-driven (reads index list from manifest or catalog). Hybrid Bicep+PS pattern: PS calls Bicep for resource shape if updated; PS handles index PUT calls + KV secret upserts + cross-resource wiring.
    Retire 5 pre-existing per-index PS scripts + 1 Bicep deployer in the SAME PR.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Spaarke platform infrastructure engineer. Expert in PowerShell SupportsShouldProcess pattern, Azure CLI scripting, Bicep parametrization, Azure AI Search REST API.
  </role>

  <goal>
    `scripts/ai-search/Deploy-AllIndexes.ps1` operational with required params, idempotent, post-deploy invariant verifier. 5 per-index PS scripts + 1 Bicep deployer deleted in same PR.
  </goal>

  <context>
    <background>
      Current Deploy-IndexSchemas.ps1 is broken (wrong IndexMap; covers 3 of 7 indexes). FR-07 replaces it with single unified script.
      Redis project's Deploy-RedisCache.ps1 is the validated template — mirror its structure.
    </background>
    <relevant-files>
      <file>scripts/ai-search/Deploy-AllIndexes.ps1</file>
      <file>scripts/Deploy-RedisCache.ps1</file>
